Author: drusenko
Content: "Don't launch with a crappy product -- launch as soon as what you have is better than what is out there." If I remember correctly, that is advice given by Paul Buchheit.

Author: matstc
Title: the bubble cycle is replacing the business cycle

Author: samwise
Content: It's important to note that eventhough you should launch early, your product should work well and have a real benefit. too often i see startups launchs with a half-baked idea.

Author: bprater

Author: raxitsheth
Content:
Hey Hackers,

Its simple idea, like folks have Photo Blog, Video Blog, [News Blog], Tech Blog etc,... MyKavita (Kavita = Poem) is multiuser blog for Poem. Its promoting individuals about poetric creation and relavant stuff.

It is powered by wordpress, and it is crossing 1 month till launch. (we launched at BarcampTechfest @ Asia's largest techfest @ IIT-bombay india)

Would love to have your feedback on UI, tech or any other stuff relavant to MyKavita.com
